"content_rendered": "<p>已经单身很多年了，属于是那种很老实的人，从小到大都是乖乖听话，好好学习，好好工作</p>\n<p>平常工作时间比较长，没什么社交活动，一起玩的都是男性</p>\n<p>最近通过社交平台认识到了一些女生，但是不知道怎么追求比较好，想请教一下</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775610291, "replies": 59, "id": 1204183}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_large.png?m=1591791660", "name": "gts", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_normal.png?m=1591791660", "title": "全球工单系统", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/gts", "topics": 10635, "footer": "", "header": "希望这里能够为你遇到的问题找到解决方案", "title_alternative": "Global Ticket System", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_mini.png?m=1591791660", "stars": 1921, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 938, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 461023, "username": "acodermini", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/acodermini", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e7c172f73f5f06a80a2011a6be4a9904?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e7c172f73f5f06a80a2011a6be4a9904?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e7c172f73f5f06a80a2011a6be4a9904?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1577169933, "last_modified": 1577169933, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "hanxu317138", "last_touched": 1775628296, "title": "不靠谱梯子曝光", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1204209", "created": 1775613904, "deleted": 0, "content": "有没有人用 naiko.cloud 的梯子，太不不靠谱了，大家千万别买，频繁出问题，还没免费的靠谱", "content_rendered": "<p>有没有人用 naiko.cloud 的梯子，太不不靠谱了，大家千万别买，频繁出问题，还没免费的靠谱</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775617150, "replies": 51, "id": 1204209}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1751718333", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1751718333", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 238042, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4479, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 233315, "username": "might1", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/might1", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0509/1572/233315_mini.png?m=1774832552", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0509/1572/233315_normal.png?m=1774832552", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0509/1572/233315_large.png?m=1774832552", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0509/1572/233315_xlarge.png?m=1774832552", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0509/1572/233315_xxlarge.png?m=1774832552", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0509/1572/233315_xxxlarge.png?m=1774832552", "created": 1496225947, "last_modified": 1774832552, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Dogergo", "last_touched": 1775628680, "title": "鼻炎有什么你亲身体验过好用的工具或治疗方案吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1204098", "created": 1775556528, "deleted": 0, "content": "印象中有一次感冒长期未治愈，后面经常堵去看医生就说我是过敏性鼻炎。\r\n十几年后偶然看到文章加上问 AI ，发现自己其实是血管运动性鼻炎。\r\n不知道是环境的原因，还是遗传的原因，自己的小孩好像也有点鼻炎了。\r\n不论什么鼻炎，几乎没法完全治愈了，目前了解到比较好的治疗方案就是生理盐水洗鼻子。但是坚持洗鼻子太难了，准备工作一堆，洗完后也要冲洗晾晒工具。自己坚持了几个月确实有缓解，后面没有坚持下去。\r\n我就想问问有没有 v 友有什么好用的洗鼻子工具，或者能长期坚持下来更好的方案，自己亲身体验过的，当然也乐见大家分享缓解鼻塞、流鼻涕流清涕的好办法。", "content_rendered": "<p>印象中有一次感冒长期未治愈，后面经常堵去看医生就说我是过敏性鼻炎。\n十几年后偶然看到文章加上问 AI ，发现自己其实是血管运动性鼻炎。\n不知道是环境的原因，还是遗传的原因，自己的小孩好像也有点鼻炎了。\n不论什么鼻炎，几乎没法完全治愈了，目前了解到比较好的治疗方案就是生理盐水洗鼻子。但是坚持洗鼻子太难了，准备工作一堆，洗完后也要冲洗晾晒工具。自己坚持了几个月确实有缓解，后面没有坚持下去。\n我就想问问有没有 v 友有什么好用的洗鼻子工具，或者能长期坚持下来更好的方案，自己亲身体验过的，当然也乐见大家分享缓解鼻塞、流鼻涕流清涕的好办法。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775556528, "replies": 49, "id": 1204098}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_large.png?m=1751736790", "name": "claude", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_normal.png?m=1751736790", "title": "Claude", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claude", "topics": 392, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Claude", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_mini.png?m=1751736790", "stars": 398, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 727749, "username": "Leroy666", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Leroy666", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/980e/1337/727749_mini.png?m=1760834540", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/980e/1337/727749_normal.png?m=1760834540", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/980e/1337/727749_large.png?m=1760834540", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/980e/1337/727749_xlarge.png?m=1760834540", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/980e/1337/727749_xxlarge.png?m=1760834540", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/980e/1337/727749_xxxlarge.png?m=1760834540", "created": 1735561107, "last_modified": 1760834540, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "xiaoxu1118", "last_touched": 1775594315, "title": "有偿付费求 Claude 稳定运行经验", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1204060", "created": 1775550491, "deleted": 0, "content": "被 Claude 第一次封号之前，我用得非常放肆，有时候魔法没挂上被他弹出网页说地区不支持都没事，\r\n直到 3.18 那天被封了之后就连续被封，\r\n\r\n美国静态住宅 IP 试了、指纹浏览器也试了、\r\n淘宝买的 pro 号活不过两天,我实在是没招了。\r\n\r\n明明我的用量也不大，就是一些文字工作。\r\n\r\n求程序员大佬们给我出出主意。\r\n\r\n愿意付费咨询。", "content_rendered": "<p>被 Claude 第一次封号之前，我用得非常放肆，有时候魔法没挂上被他弹出网页说地区不支持都没事，\n直到 3.18 那天被封了之后就连续被封，</p>\n<p>美国静态住宅 IP 试了、指纹浏览器也试了、\n淘宝买的 pro 号活不过两天,我实在是没招了。</p>\n<p>明明我的用量也不大，就是一些文字工作。</p>\n<p>求程序员大佬们给我出出主意。</p>\n<p>愿意付费咨询。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775550491, "replies": 48, "id": 1204060}]